                  <t:ab type="history">Gatar. 

A small church dedicated to <t:persName type="tabot" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4306GabraMa">Gabra Manfas Qǝddus</t:persName> is located in the vicinity.</t:ab>
                  <t:ab type="description">
