                        </t:graphic>
                     </t:figure>17 Mss., one scroll photographed: <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp001">EHPP-001</t:ref> “Dawit”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp002">EHPP-002</t:ref> “Acts of the Apostles”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp003">EHPP-003</t:ref> “Homily on the Saviour of the World”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp004">EHPP-004</t:ref> “Vita of Mäzgäbä Śǝllase”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp005">EHPP-005</t:ref> “Homily on St. Michael”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp006">EHPP-006</t:ref> “Vita of Gäbrä Mänfäs Qǝddus”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp007">EHPP-007</t:ref> “Vita of John the Baptist, Miracles of John the Baptist”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp008">EHPP-008</t:ref> “Homily on St. Michael”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp009">EHPP-009</t:ref> “The Book of Baptism”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp010">EHPP-010</t:ref> “Synaxarion (March-September)”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp011">EHPP-011</t:ref> “Acts of the Apostles”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp012">EHPP-012</t:ref> “Four Gospels”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp013">EHPP-013</t:ref> “Book of the Funeral Rite”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp014">EHPP-014</t:ref> “The Loosening of the Spells”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp015">EHPP-015</t:ref> “Missal”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp016">EHPP-016</t:ref> “Homily on the Sabbath of Christians”; <t:ref type="mss" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/ESehpp017">EHPP-017</t:ref> “The Bandlet of Righteous”.</t:ab>
         
